  <ns4442:title xmlns:ns4442="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Tactics used to realize modifiability</ns4442:title>
  <ns4443:para xmlns:ns4443="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    The core strategies driving modifiability are
    <ns4444:itemizedlist xmlns:ns4444="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      <ns4445:listitem xmlns:ns4445="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns4446:para xmlns:ns4446="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">complexity reduction,</ns4446:para></ns4445:listitem>
      <ns4447:listitem xmlns:ns4447="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns4448:para xmlns:ns4448="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">localized maintenance, and</ns4448:para></ns4447:listitem>
      <ns4449:listitem xmlns:ns4449="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns4450:para xmlns:ns4450="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">late binding.</ns4450:para></ns4449:listitem>
    </ns4444:itemizedlist>
    To this end a wide range of tactics can be used (see
    <ns4451:xref xmlns:ns4451="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" linkend="resources.information.concepts.architecture.qualityAttributes.modifiability.tactics_fig"/>).
  </ns4443:para>
  
